channel.title: ----Xcollision---- Development Team Needed (317)
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/ionac1.gif[/img] thanks to- krackkid our awsome graphic dev (317)
[size=14pt](SERVER)[/size] Welcome to the development of Xcollision, We are going to be a nice community with lots of players once we get finished. We are going to try to get sponserd after we get enough players that we get a vps so no one has to host. This source/server is pkplanet and going to be turned inside out and modifyed big time. We will have skill capes with proper 100% emotes, Working d claws that hit x4, some customs not to many or that will ruin economy. Fully working skills ( except construction unless it is possible). 100% combat along with range mage. all GWD bosses. Jad and mabey a few custom bosses. There is so much more that will happen it will take too long to write so im cutting it short.
[size=18pt]What We are Aiming For[/size] We are going to aim to be one of the best servers out there, if not we will have to work our way up. The server is going to be on 24/7 and have a 15+player average online. more to be added soon
[size=14pt]What we are looking for in people[/size] We are looking for people that will dedicate some of there time into the server at least 4+hours a week at the lease not much as there is 7 days in a week. Please if you apply try to spend some time on if you get it. We are also looking for people that will that are kind and dont back stab or anything polit is a proper word for it and generous. There is no age limit but We really need mature people for this no 11 year olds that will goof off. although i said no age limit im going to recemend the age most people should be is ----------13+-------------
This is a respectful community if you share any work done here or give it to friends you will be removed.
Dev Team *Leader AND CODER* ApocalypsePK web devo-abdelwassa web devo-Paymon Server Coder- Server Coder- client coder-TubeFish client coder- OPEN Beta tester-OPEN Beta tester-OPEN Graphics Dev- krackkid
If you want to be a server coder please apply with exp dont be a beginner. at least 2 months of coding exp any less dont apply this is serious.
If you want to be a client coder apply but you must know what you are doing, if you dont have much exp dont bother please and apply for something else(acceptions can be made)
If you want to apply for a Web Devo Make Have Exp as all the others and you must have made a website/ forums before.
Beta Tester? We only need 1-2 for now but there will be a beta when we get rolling but this is for our two main beta testers so apply for it if you know how to find glitches and bugs ect.
----STAFF--- This is something that will not be talked about on the forums as it can be against the rules so when you see the server up(not for a while) go to those forums and look and apply there
